     "Palette Performance: 8-bit mode (1 argument) is a fast C-array lookup; 24-bit mode (3 arguments) requires expensive string formatting and GTK tag lookups.",
     "Latent Win Conditions: Ensure end-game logic checks for active animation timers (M_Explode_Timer) so players see the final explosion before the win screen.",
     "Coordinate Timing: Erase must happen at old coordinates before updating global Y or reversing direction."
