     "Variable Audit: Cross-reference existing 'def_var' lists before creating new logic-checks to avoid colliding with speed/timing variables like 'logic_sum'.",
     "Boundary Guarding: Stop projectiles 1 line early (DISP_Y_MAX - 1) to protect HUD/Score text from space-erasure."
